graph TD
    A[Child Adds Wishlist Item] -->|POST /wishlist| B(Wishlist Table)
    B --> C[System Calculates Progress]
    C --> D[Child Tracks Progress]
    D -->|GET /wishlist/progress| E(Progress Bar)
    E --> F{Target Reached?}
    F -->|Yes| G{Notify Parent & Child}
    F -->|No| D
    G --> H[Parent Fulfills Wish]
    H -->|PATCH /wishlist| I[Mark as Completed]
    I --> J[Update Child Dashboard]
